{"tid":1278621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急 唔該入黎","createTime":"2019-07-02T13:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T15:25:45.000Z","uid":12970,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"69dd552ff6be8ba2d90ba2985f46cd83da67a68c","tid":1278621,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:21:47.000Z","msg":"過左琴晚之後到今朝開始出現大批三毛開po帶風向<br />\n共媒都開始造新聞打輿論戰<br />\n改圖抹黑分化全部出哂黎<br />\n<br />\n當然大家都知係on9先信唔撚洗理<br />\n我見大家都係笑下就算<br />\n但重點就係<br />\n佢哋對象就正是嗰啲on9<br />\n藍絲<br />\n廢老<br />\n務求做到全城批鬥抗爭義士<br />\n再分化<br />\n<br />\n我唔知係咪我諗太多<br />\n但一直由佢地我怕會不可收拾<br />\n 希望大家真係諗下"},{"pid":"594d040d564fe296149dc538fbc0ebe777fbcd54","tid":1278621,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:22:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"731e12c3b55aa8e7040df7fdcb4bdf339640cfa8","tid":1278621,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:22:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b6f44f648c54aa5aa0033b7671f9f83097f204e","tid":1278621,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:22:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8aeb5fe97d65df2ab50f4ac092989494e5aad2e2","tid":1278621,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:23:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"216a339654cd161355ddd2145189fc27f03e30a2","tid":1278621,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:23:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81be47bd15500dda10cb88843bca64b0477aaac8","tid":1278621,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:23:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d8f925fee9a2c6621a0e4ecd095aa7375193633","tid":1278621,"uid":49226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:24:08.000Z","msg":"咁有什麼良策？"},{"pid":"259b16bfad5e407fbfc7add45edcd056f7efa718","tid":1278621,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d8f925fee9a2c6621a0e4ecd095aa7375193633","tid":1278621,"uid":49226,